ddns

A simple, extensible, cross-distribution, cross-platform dynamic DNS updater
written in Python.

WEB HOME:
	http://git.ipfire.org/?p=ddns.git;a=summary

BUG TRACKER:
	https://bugzilla.ipfire.org/

	Product: DDNS Updater

